        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3057767038" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5671597004823317131">In this quiet novel, five individuals, each dealing with their own painful personal tragedy, are unexpectedly brought together during the Christmas season in the Scottish countryside—though they&apos;ve decided not to celebrate the holiday; it&apos;s too painful this year. But redemption is found in surprising places, and in the midst of so much loss, love and redemption emerge. This book was a delightful surprise; I enjoyed it so much.</span>
  <span id="freeText5671597004823317131" style="display:none">In this quiet novel, five individuals, each dealing with their own painful personal tragedy, are unexpectedly brought together during the Christmas season in the Scottish countryside—though they've decided not to celebrate the holiday; it's too painful this year. But redemption is found in surprising places, and in the midst of so much loss, love and redemption emerge. This book was a delightful surprise; I enjoyed it so much.</span>
