           <span class="uitext reviewText">everyone </span></div>

          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Relyn by: </span>
      I have been a fan of Rosamunde Pilcher for years
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1060439-relyn?shelf=audiobooks">audiobooks</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1060439-relyn?shelf=2011-reread">2011-reread</a>, 
